OL,5,CINTERNATIONAL GREEN BULLETIN           
OL,6,F                                       
OL,7,C CYPRUS:GEnvironmentalists in Turkish-
OL,8, held northern Cyprus are threatening to
OL,9, sue over a plan to export wild donkeys 
OL,10, from the island's north-eastern Karpass
OL,11, peninsula.                             
OL,13, Kenan Akin, responsible for agriculture
OL,14, in the area, says the donkeys were     
OL,15, damaging crops.                        
OL,17, But Boysan Boyra of Greenpeace says:   
OL,18, "We won't allow them to take a single  
OL,19, donkey from Karpass!"                  
