OL,5,CINTERNATIONAL GREEN BULLETIN           
OL,6,F                                       
OL,7,C SWITZERLAND:GSweden has urged the    
OL,8, five major nuclear powers to take their
OL,9, forces off alert to lower the risk of  
OL,10, an accidental weapons launch.          
OL,12, In a speech to the Conference on       
OL,13, Disarmament in Geneva, Swedish foreign 
OL,14, minister Lena Hjelm-Wallen demanded    
OL,15, talks on halting production of nuclear 
OL,16, bomb-making equipment.                 
OL,18, She also called for a total ban on     
OL,19, landmines.                             
