OL,5,CINTERNATIONAL GREEN BULLETIN           
OL,6,F                                       
OL,7,C CALIFORNIA:GA new fuel cell developed
OL,8, in California has raised hopes of a    
OL,9, clean source of electricity provided   
OL,10, directly from methanol.                
OL,12, The device works by taking hydrogen    
OL,13, from the methanol, passing it through a
OL,14, membrane and combining it with oxygen  
OL,15, to produce water and electricity.      
OL,17, The developers, Jet Propulsion         
OL,18, Laboratory, say they hope to make cells
OL,19, large enough to power cars.            
