OL,5,CINTERNATIONAL GREEN BULLETIN           
OL,6,F                                       
OL,7,C KENYA:GUp to 30% of the country's    
OL,8, livestock has been wiped out after     
OL,9, three consecutive rainy seasons failed 
OL,10, in 18 months.                          
OL,12, A spokesman from Oxfam says December's 
OL,13, short rains failed entirely, starving  
OL,14, people, cattle, goats, and camels.     
OL,16, The charity warns: "We have a serious  
OL,17, scenario moving towards an emergency." 
