OL,5,CINTERNATIONAL GREEN BULLETIN           
OL,6,F                                       
OL,7,C JAPAN:GAn explosion at a nuclear fuel
OL,8, processing plant near Tokyo may have   
OL,9, released radioactive material.         
OL,11, An official from the plant at Tokai in 
OL,12, Ibaraki prefecture says no-one was     
OL,13, injured, but there "are fears that     
OL,14, radioactive materials may have spread".
OL,16, However the local government has not   
OL,17, issued an emergency evacuation order to
OL,18, the 30,000 inhabitants of the small    
OL,19, seaside village.                       
