OL,5,CINTERNATIONAL GREEN BULLETIN           
OL,6,F                                       
OL,7,C FLORIDA:GA whale has become the      
OL,8, unlikely victim of violence in         
OL,9, Key-West, south Florida.               
OL,11, A four-tonne Minke whale that beached  
OL,12, on Big Pine Key was found to have five 
OL,13, bullets in it.                         
OL,15, Becky Barron, director of the Wildlife 
OL,16, Rescue of the Florida Keys says she    
OL,17, believed boaters had opened fire on it,
OL,18, adding: "We're pretty amazed that      
OL,19, people out there are doing this!"      
